&quot;It is always a pleasure to be in the presence of such creatures of high esteem. Throughout my young life I have heard many tales concerning elves and are greatly in awe of them,&quot; She turned to the other travelers.<br>
&quot;Now, for the introductions. This man you see in the silver armor,&quot;She motioned to Timothy,&quot;goes by the name of Timothy,an ex-gladiator. The fellow standing beside him,&quot;she pointed to Cryrid,&quot; is know as Cryrid, and has the best aim with a knife I have seen, though is a bit quick to throw. Next to him is Cameron, though silent is quite a fighter. The elf you see goes by the name of Elil, and is exelent at catching thieves. The man you see carriying the pole-arm is Van Eyck, and might I say, he can wield his weapon with ease,&quot; She turned back to the trio of elves.<br>
&quot;I am Caprice Maltempo, mistress of illusions-&quot;<br>
Anlore's father waved his hand, stopping Caprice in mid-sentence.&quot;Please, if you will. Tell us the details of you adventure so far. Though we know of the quest, the smaller items have escaped our knowledge,&quot; Caprice nodded and began to relate the tail with help from others.<br>
&quot;Now, you seem rather worried about the king's son getting the throne. He may be mean and all, but he's just a normal being,right?&quot;Caprice asked.<br>
